title: Reds Tube Bar (Bum Bar Bastards) prank calls
description:
Been looking for the Red's Tube Bar (aka Bum Bar Bastards) tapes recently but no luck (lots of dead ends). Uncovered this audio found years ago on suprnova - might have been put together by the Tube Bar prankster (Jim Davidson). Sorry, don't know the original track names - if there are any. Tracks 2 and 4 aren't phone calls but the latter is definitely a good name for a band.  Tracks 1 and 6 are the real deal though!

128k stereo mp3 
Track 1 - Red's Tube Bar (24:53)  
Track 2 - sound of an extended shit (3:29)  
Track 3 - Calling some other guy (5:38)  
Track 4 - Traveling Dingleberries ? (49 secs)  
Track 5 - Calling a foul-mouthed woman (3:39)  
Track 6 - More Tube Bar (11:16)  
Total: 49:44  

Thanks to the original uploader.
